com.ipt.ebsa.manage.deploy.comprelease

Class CompositeReleasePhase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ipt.ebsa.manage.deploy.comprelease.CompositeReleasePhase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Deployment

    public class CompositeReleasePhase
extends java.lang.Object
implements Deployment
    Class gathers the deployment data for a phase of a composite release deployment, that is, a collection of independent applications that can be combined and deployed together.
